      <scopecontent id="aspace_dcfcdba19b55a9ed7099d90d96f35f4c">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence, budget materials, and subject files documenting student activities and accomplishments, scholarships, athletics, and student employment.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <bioghist id="aspace_9e2fd6d8d99429c9522c7076e3cba47b">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>The title "Master" for chief executive officers of residential colleges was changed to "Head of College" in April of 2016.</p>  
      </bioghist>
